data.description: Welcome to the epitome of cozy farmhouse living in this charming 1200 square foot bungalow. Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this property offers not only a delightful home but also a wealth of possibilities with its large 2-car garage and workshop, all wrapped in a fully fenced yard for your privacy and peace of mind. The heart of this home is the brand new kitchen, thoughtfully designed with meticulous attention to detail. Crisp white shaker cabinets, gleaming quartz countertops, and  tile backsplash create a fresh and airy atmosphere. Situated in a friendly community, this home offers not only a beauty but also proximity to local amenities, schools, and parks. It's the perfect blend of style and functionality, providing a peaceful retreat where you can truly embrace country living
